sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as Next.js Reader
    participant API as NestJS Chat API / Socket
    participant Queue as BullMQ
    participant Worker as Persistence Worker
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    Note left of User: Debounced Scroll / Blur

    User->>API: HTTP POST /rooms/:roomId/read

    alt Strategy: Direct Persistence
        activate API

        API->>DB: Persist last-read cursor
        API-->>User: 200 OK
    else Strategy: Write-Behind
        API->>Queue: Buffer latest read cursor
        API->>Queue: Mark read state dirty
        API-->>User: 200 OK
        
        deactivate API

        activate Worker

        Note over Queue, DB: Background Recurring Sync (SYNC_LAST_READ_JOB)
        Worker->>Queue: Pick up dirty read cursors
        Worker->>DB: Persist read cursors as batch

        Worker->>Queue: Re-enqueue SYNC_LAST_READ_JOB

        deactivate Worker
    end
    
    Note left of User: Read state reflected on next sync

    
